'''Colleen Denney''' is a professor of gender and [[women's studies]] at the [[University of Wyoming]].<ref>[http://www.uwyo.edu/wmst/faculty_staff/denney_colleen.html Colleen Denney.] University of Wyoming. Retrieved 22 May 2015.</ref> She is a specialist in British women artists of the Victorian era.

Denney's ''The Grosvenor Gallery: A Palace of Art in Victorian England'' (1996) was the first detailed study of the [[Grosvenor Gallery]].<ref>[http://yalepress.yale.edu/book.asp?isbn=9780300067521 ''The Grosvenor Gallery A Palace of Art in Victorian England''.] Yale University Press. Retrieved 22 May 2015.</ref>

